The original data files from which the differential expression statistics are calculated from are held in the 
[[http://www.ebi.ac.uk/arrayexpress/ ArrayExpress Archive]].  You can link to the original data for any experiment by clicking on the experiment accession number e.g. E-TABM-1216 from the
experiment page in the Atlas.

